Map {
User Stories {
Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view orders that are not supported by the music application.
Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select a travel time for my music application.
Create Playlists: As a user, I want to be able to create playlists with my favorite songs.
Share Music: As a user, I want to be able to share music with my friends.
Search Music: As a user, I want to be able to search for music by artist, genre, or title.
Save Music: As a user, I want to be able to save music to my library.
Organize Music: As a user, I want to be able to organize my music library.
}

Features {
Music Player: As a user, I want to be able to play music from the application.
Music Library: As a user, I want to be able to access my music library.
Music Recommendations: As a user, I want to be able to receive music recommendations.
Music Streaming: As a user, I want to be able to stream music from the application.
}

UI/UX {
User Interface: As a user, I want to be able to navigate the application easily.
User Experience: As a user, I want to have a positive experience while using the application.
}
}
